data.description: Seller offering $15,000 for closing costs or rate buy down!! MOVE IN READY ON A CORNER LOT!! Exquisite upstairs main home is 3BR/2BTH 2069 sq. ft. with a grand front porch and luxury accents and attention to detail throughout- chandeliers, canned lighting, crown molding and gleaming wood floors. Enjoy the spacious laundry/utility room and detached garage. Two apartments downstairs each 2BR/1BTH offer excellent rental income opportunities to help pay your mortgage! All three units have NO CARPET, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops. There is an abundance of outdoor space to enjoy with a ground level fenced courtyard. Freshly paved roads on both Bruxelles St. and Industry St. Minutes to the Fairgrounds, City Park, and 610 for commuting. Ask about new low down payment loan opportunities for owner occupied homes!
